      <content><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Open the <a title="Demo application" href="%(link0)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">demo 3 app</a>.</li>
<li>The app shows the same content used multiple times in different display variations (image left, image right, only image, etc.).</li>
<li>Open the same page in the <a title="Editable web view" href="%(link1)">OpenCms page editor</a>.</li>
<li>In the page editor, open the element settings dialog (requires login).</li>
<li>Change the element settings in the dialog, click save, and see how the changes are reflected in the demo application.</li>
<li>Read more about the technical details of the JSON page handler in the <a href="%(link2)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OpenCms JSON API documentation</a>.</li>
<li>Have a look at the <a href="%(link3)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">source code of the demo 3 app</a>.</li>
</ul>]]></content>
